Vatom **  plist,
int *  pnlist,
int *  pnatoms
) 
 

Get a the next available atom storage location, increasing the storage space if necessary. Return VNULL if something goes wrong.

Parameters:
pnlist  Pointer to existing list of atoms
pnatoms  Size of existing list, may be changed Existing number of atoms in list; incremented before exit
